<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johann II. von Heideck</head><p>Der Rat dankt für die Vermittlung im Streit mit Hiltpolt von Fraunberg und bittet um Ansetzung eines neuen Schiedsgerichts in Berching unter Johanns Anwesenheit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_394" id="196v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_394_r2l17"><expan>Johan<ex>n</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> cʒu Heẏdeck / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_394_r2l18">Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als vvir ew nechſt <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd Jr ew der ſach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_394_r2l19">cʒwiſchen <expan>Hilpolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd vnſer <expan>angenome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_394_r2l20">des vvir <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒemal <expan>fleiſſigl<ex>ich</ex></expan> dancken / Alſo laſſen vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_394_r2l21">Edell wiſſen daʒ vns hılpolt <expan>frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan> yecʒunden <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_394_r2l22">vnd vvir Jm vvıder geantwurt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> als vvir ew ſeins vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_394_r2l23">auch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>bed<ex>er</ex></expan> brief 
<del rend="strikethrough"> aſ </del> abſchrifft ſchicken <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſen</expan> ın dıeſem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_394_r2l24">brief vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr Jm vnd vns einen gemainen tag ſecʒen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_394_r2l25">vnd beſcheẏden vvöllet gen <expan>Perching<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd auch ſelber darauf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_394_r2l26">kumt / vnd wollet ew der müvve <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> dinſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_394_r2l27">vvillen nicht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>drieſſen</expan> laſſen / Als vvir ein beſunder getrawen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_394_r2l28">cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd auch cʒu allen <expan>cʒeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wılliglich vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_394_r2l29"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> vvöllen / <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in <expan>c<ex>ra</ex>ſtı<ex>n</ex>o</expan> <expan>Circ<ex>umciſionis</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>ni</expan> <expan>a<ex>nn</ex><hi rend="sup">o</hi></expan> xij<hi rend="sup">o</hi> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_394" id="196v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Johan<ex>n</ex>s</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> czu Heydeck
                    </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir ew nechst
                                <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und ir ew der sach czwischen
                                <expan>Hilpolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan> und unser
                            <expan>angenome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt, des wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> czemal <expan>fleissigl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        dancken, also lassen wir edell wissen, daz uns Hilpolt
                                <expan>Frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan> yeczunden
                                <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und wir im wider geantwurt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als wir ew seins und auch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>bed<ex>er</ex></expan> brief abschrifft schicken
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>slossen</expan> in diesem brief, und
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir im und uns einen gemainen
                        tag seczen und bescheyden wöllet gen <expan>Perching<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                        auch selber darauf kumt; und wollet ew der müwe
                            <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
                        dinst willen nicht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>driessen</expan> lassen, als wir ein
                        besunder getrawen czu <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und auch czu allen
                            <expan>czeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> williglich und
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> wöllen. <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in
                            <expan>c<ex>ra</ex>sti<ex>n</ex>o</expan>
<expan>circ<ex>umcisionis</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>ni</expan>
<expan>a<ex>nn</ex><hi rend="sup">o</hi></expan> xii<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
